            <title>[CXF-6851] JAXRS 2 Feature not supported on server side?</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-6851</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hi&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;maybe I missed something but seems DynamicFeatures are supported on server side through @Provider but Features (JAXRS2 ones, not CXF ones) are not. This prevents to reuse some logic like Moxy JAXRS integration for instance which provides a hidden (for end user) ContextProvider&amp;lt;JAXBContext&amp;gt; through a Feature.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
