                            <comment id="15217830" author="sergey_beryozkin" created="Wed, 30 Mar 2016 11:42:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes, Feature was introduced while we were working on the client API, so I was not really focusing on adding it to the server, except for DynamicFeature so as a workaround, you can register Feature from within DynamicFeature. Not sure though about registering providers like ContextProvider from Feature(Context), many of those methods have priorities accepted and it only makes sense for the 2.0 filters/interceptors, it is confusing... &lt;/p&gt;
